scene.message:
Maki: Hey, hey, Inaba's at the{nl}
police station, right? Let's{nl}
hurry and go save him!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Man, what a lame shop{nl}
though!{waitkey}{clearbox}If it were me, I'd remodel it{nl}
into an open-air cafe!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That shopkeeper seems{nl}
to suspect us.{waitkey}{clearbox}But with these strange powers{nl}
of ours, are we still truly{nl}
human, I wonder?{waitkey}What do you think?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: There are some{nl}
surprisingly calm people{nl}
around. I'm impressed.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: So {ctl0f:1}, you were{nl}
into this kind of thing!{nl}
Aw, that's adorable!{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: ...{wait_fr:16}Are you a{nl}
real human?{wait_fr:32} Well, if you're a{nl}
customer, you're welcome.{waitkey}{ret}
